title: Amy's Kids First American Thanksgiving + Bobby Gets Negative Tweet From Popular Celebrity
itunes:title: Amy's Kids First American Thanksgiving + Bobby Gets Negative Tweet From Popular Celebrity
description:
Amy's kids experienced their first American Thanksgiving dinner since being adopted from Haiti. Bobby responds to Neil Patrick Harris' negative tweet about him winning 'Dancing With The Stars'. Plus, someone snuck in Bobby's dressing room at his comedy show.
